column5: 第一场结束; Man starts singing;
第二场结束; 2. Auction ends. Ted bought Joey;
第三场结束; 3. End of scene 3. Rose leaves to scold Ted;
Albert walk backwards towards Joey. ; 小马开始吃燕麦;
4. End of scene 4. (0:16:37). Albert picks up the bucket;
变大马; Joey becomes a big horse;
阿尔伯特再次骑大马出现; Albert appears riding on Joey;
第六场结束; End of scene 6. Ted leaves to go for a drink. (0:22:22);
Albert pats on Joey and say he will not sell it;
第七场结束，鹅啄门，观众笑; End of Scene 7. (0:24:45). Albert exits;
End of scene 8 (0:29:47). Rose lets go of Albert's hand and said, ' don't grow up'. ;
乔伊第一次成功套上轭; Joey wears harness;
乔伊拉不动犁跪下; Music stops;
Song begins. ; 乔伊拉动了犁，歌声开始;
泰德打赌成功; Everyone cheers. Joey reaches the end of line;
第十场结束; End of scene 10. Rose leaves the stage. (0:42:12);
Joey walks to the centre of the stage. Drum rolls;
阿尔伯特和乔伊告别中途被强迫分开; Albert says goodbye to Joey. ;
枪响，乔伊被吓到; First gun triggers;
End of scene 13. Captain salutes each other.  (0:56:59);
第十四场结束; End of scene 14. Boat scene and song ends(0:58:01);
End of scene 15. Soldiers reply together. (1:00:40);
第十六场结束; End of scene 16. end of song. (01:03:51);
